These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, project-manager, dancer, librarian
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, dancing, card-games, cooking
1. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
4. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the project-manager##1
6. the dancer is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Job      | librarian  | nurse | project-manager  | dancer |
| Hobby   | card-games | cooking      | magic-tricks | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, cola, water
City: paris, berlin, marseilles, liverpool
1. the person drinking juice is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to liverpool##2
2. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person drinking water##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | water | cola | juice   | milk |
| City           | marseilles      | paris    | berlin | liverpool      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, traveling, magic-tricks, singing
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, amber, mauve, green
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who likes amber##1
2. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
4. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
5. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Hobby        | traveling | fishing | magic-tricks     | singing |
| Color   | amber  | green   | mauve | azure    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, baccarat, siglo, bolivar
4 different games are played: snooker, go, scrabble, poker
1. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
3. the chaman-smoker is between the person playing poker and the person playing go##2
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
5. the person playing poker is the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Cigar         | siglo | chaman | baccarat | bolivar |
| Game   | poker   | scrabble     | go    | snooker       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
City: berlin, boston, rome, new-york
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, skydiving, cooking, collecting
1. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
3. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| City          | rome | new-york   | berlin   | boston    |
| Hobby   | skydiving  | collecting | sudoku | cooking |

