.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
City: edinburgh, paris, liverpool, san-francisco
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, house, indie, hip-hop
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
3. the fan of hip-hop is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the fan of indie##2
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| City           | edinburgh | paris | san-francisco | liverpool |
| Music-Genre   | indie        | hip-hop     | blues       | house   |

