.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, satire, western, scientific
House: cape-cod, gothic-revival, art-deco, craftsman
1. the gothic-revival house is the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching satire movies and the art-deco house##2
3. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4
4. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
5. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
6. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | thriller  | western  | scientific   |
| House           | craftsman  | cape-cod | art-deco | gothic-revival |

