.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, gospel, salsa, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, baseball, cycling, handball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the fan of trance is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
4. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of trance##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | trance | salsa     | blues   |
| Sport    | handball | baseball  | cycling | basketball |

