.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, january, august, december
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, amber, mauve, white
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5
5. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
6. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Birthday   | may | august | december   | january |
| Color       | emerald       | mauve   | white | amber |

