.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, van, tram
There 4 different types of food: pepper, strawberry, apricot, kiwi
1. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
2. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
3. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
4. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person eating kiwi##5
5. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Transport   | car | van       | bike   | tram        |
| Food      | strawberry  | kiwi | pepper | apricot |

