.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, february, june, march
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, fantasy, horror
1. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
2. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
5. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
6. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
7. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person watching drama movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | november | february   | june | march     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | drama | fantasy  | horror |

