.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, snowmobile, jet-ski
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, blend, game, bolivar
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
4. the person driving the car is the game-smoker##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
6. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | car | snowmobile        | jet-ski        | motorbike |
| Cigar         | game  | bolivar | dunhill | blend |

