.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia, light-blue, aquamarine
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hedgehog, hamster, turtle
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
3. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
5. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color         | light-blue | aquamarine | fuchsia | purple |
| Pet   | guinea-pig     | turtle  | hedgehog  | hamster    |

