2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
3. the electrician is on the left of the engineer##1
4. the engineer is the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
6. the electrician is on the left or right of the coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | mirinda | coffee | 7up |
| Job   | architect | coach | electrician   | engineer  |

