.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, peas, apple, pomegranate
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, lizard, rat
1. the person eating pomegranate is between the person eating apple and the person eating peas##2
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
3. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
4. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
5. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food   | watermelon | apple  | pomegranate      | peas |
| Pet     | lizard    | rat | bird | guinea-pig   |

