4. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
6. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to venice and the person watching adventure movies##2
7. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
