2. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan of techno##5
3. the fan of house is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5
4. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the coach##5
5. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of metal##1
6. the firefighter is between the photographer and the fan of metal##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Job      | teacher     | photographer | firefighter     | coach |
| Music-Genre   | house | techno  | salsa | metal        |

