.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, go, chess
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, skydiving, photography, hiking
1. the person playing canasta is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person playing monopoly##2
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
3. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game         | go   | chess   | canasta       | monopoly   |
| Hobby   | photography | skydiving | card-games | hiking |

