.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, metal, gospel, folk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, martial-arts, superhero, scientific
1. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
5. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
6. the fan of pop is between the fan of folk and the person watching romance movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre        | metal     | folk | pop | gospel |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | scientific | martial-arts      | romance        |

 